title: Bright One Bedroom at Parkway West *$1,000 Off First Month's Rent!*
posting_body: ['4556 46th Avenue S - 210 | Minneapolis, MN 55406', 'Available: Now!', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Available Now!', 'A bright, sunny 1BR with a view at Parkway West Apartments.', "Sign a lease and get $1,000 off your first month's rent!", 'Your new neighborhood is at the corner of 46th Ave and E 46th Street in beautiful Highland Park.', 'Steps away from Minnehaha Falls Regional Park, Pavilion, and Band Shell.', 'Shops, restaurants, and trails are right outside your doorstep, if you enjoy an active lifestyle you will feel right at home at Parkway West Apartments!', 'The amazing view from this second-floor apartment home overlooks Minnehaha Park!', 'This Bright one-bedroom features a gorgeous Euro-Style kitchen with a dishwasher, a movable center island, with the convenience of an in-unit washer and dryer!', 'Enjoy the open great room with large windows bringing in an abundance of natural light and beauty from the Park!', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Fitness Center', 'Community lounge and patio', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 718', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,425.00', 'Available: Now!', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
